    <article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6529998">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Square Enix released <a href="https://www.amazon.com/DRAGON-QUEST-HD-2D-Remake-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0D71HX7PY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Quest 3 HD-2D Remake</a> last year, offering a modern way to relive the iconic RPG. The company is now gearing up to launch a series of <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0DTJF9V24,B0DTJFDVQV,B0DTJFNWCS,B0DTJFHXDL&amp;tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Quest 3 Pixelights</a> on September 24, all four of which are now available for preorder. These official Square Enix products offer a unique way to illuminate your game room, each based on the likeness of various characters from the original NES version of the classic RPG.</p><p>Each Pixelight requires three AAA batteries, so consider picking up the affordable <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Amazon-Basics-AAA-High-Performance-36/dp/B00LH3DMUO?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Basics AAA Battery Pack (36-Count)</a> for just $13.82. They come with a 10-year shelf life and should be good for all your electronics beyond these Pixelights.</p><p>If you’ve yet to play <a href="https://www.amazon.com/DRAGON-QUEST-HD-2D-Remake-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0D71HX7PY?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Quest 3 HD-2D Remake</a>, it's on sale at Amazon. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/DRAGON-QUEST-HD-2D-Remake-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0D71HX7PY?tag=gamespot-promos-2" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Xbox Series X</a> version is the cheapest at $46.54 (was $60), though there are also nice discounts for <a href="https://www.amazon.com/DRAGON-QUEST-HD-2D-Remake-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0D71SHR5B?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Switch</a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/DRAGON-QUEST-HD-2D-Remake-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0D71JQXR4?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">PS5</a>.</p><p>Beyond the Pixelights, there are a few other Dragon Quest items for fans to check out. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dragon-Quest-Illustrations-30th-Anniversary/dp/1974703908?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Quest Illustrations: 30th Anniversar</a>y hardcover book is on sale for $20 (was $35), and since it’s packed with 240 pages of illustrations and designs, it’s a cool way to go behind the scenes. There’s also a <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06XSGCHZP?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Dragon Quest X Tarot Card Pack</a> with 22 large Arcana cards, each featuring colorful artwork from the series. Typically sold for $26.65, the pack is discounted to $20.47.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/1972-piece-lego-mario-kart-display-model-revealed-on-mario-day/1100-6530000/">1,972-Piece Lego Mario Kart Display Model Revealed On Mario Day</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/suikoden-hd-remaster-collection-is-steeply-discounted-for-pc-on-launch-day/1100-6526150/">Suikoden HD Remaster Collection Is Steeply Discounted For PC On Launch Day</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/zelda-master-sword-replica-on-sale-for-big-discount-at-amazon/1100-6523376/">Zelda Master Sword Replica On Sale For Big Discount At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/spider-man-x-magic-the-gathering-trading-card-set-is-available-to-preorder/1100-6529819/">Spider-Man X Magic: The Gathering Trading Card Set Is Available To Preorder</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/the-biggest-upcoming-games-that-you-can-preorder-now/2900-6285/">The Biggest Upcoming Games That You Can Preorder Now</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/sandisk-1-5tb-microsd-card-is-steeply-discounted-at-amazon-expand-your-steam-deck-storage/1100-6527841/">SanDisk 1.5TB MicroSD Card Is Steeply Discounted At Amazon - Expand Your Steam Deck Storage</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-series-x-s-owners-can-save-big-on-western-digitals-1tb-expansion-card/1100-6527818/">Xbox Series X|S Owners Can Save Big On Western Digital's 1TB Expansion Card</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-exclusive-pokemon-tcg-premium-collection-gets-huge-limited-time-discount/1100-6528386/">Amazon-Exclusive Pokemon TCG Premium Collection Gets Huge Limited-Time Discount</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
